latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling a Sharara in five ways✨🥻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Since Sharara pants are back in trend I made an IGTV on its styling in five ways. These pants are fitted on top followed by the flare at the bottom. Depending on the styling, you can wear them on casual days and even parties/functions.

Look 1 : Wearing a solid short kurti with these pants. You can wear the outfit at small functions or get together party.

Look 2 : Wearing a cami red colored top with the Sharara pants in order to give a contrasting look to the outfit. The outfit is perfect for college events.

Look 3 : Wearing a dress as top wear with Sharara pants and completed the look with a heavy dupatta. This makes the whole outfit elegant and glam, and it is perfect for attending weddings, functions and parties.

Look 4 : Wearing a bralette top and layered a heavy black dupatta giving it an Indo-western look. Added a choker and earrings to complete the look. The outfit is super glam and is perfect for parties, functions and weddings.

Look 5 : Wearing a long kurti with the pants and completed the look with a silver neckpiece and earrings. The outfit is perfect to wear at college and even office. 

So, that was my take on styling a sharara depending upon my interests and creativity. But you can style it in your ways too. Hope you will like this video and give immense love and support to me.

Song : Yes or No (Jass Manak)

If you find the video a good one then do like, comment and share. It would mean a lot to me.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling one black dress in five ways🖤✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A girl must have one black dress in her wardrobe. A black dress can be worn in so many ways and this video is all about that.

Look 1 : Wearing a dress with a white t-shirt and added chunky necklace to make it look classy and elegant.
Look 2 : Wearing a sheer top underneath the dress in two amazing ways.
Look 3 : Wearing a flared top over the skirt (skirt as the same black dress)
Look 4 : Wearing a white shirt over the dress and added the same chunky necklace.
Look 5 : Wearing an oversized denim dress over the dress to make it look more comfy.

Also, this video will help people who are not very comfortable in wearing sleeveless dresses.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Doing my makeup💄✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Disclaimer: I am not pro at doing makeup, it is just that I love doing makeup. I wasn’t planning on putting this because I am afraid of how people will react and might say different things. But for today I didn’t have anything to post so gathering the courage to post this. 

This video is about how I do my makeup when I am going out. On regular days, I don’t put foundation, most of the times not even concealer. My skin is normal and I personally don’t like putting heavy base on regular days. But ya there are certain products that I can’t refuse and that includes blush and lipstick. Actually, the whole process depends on the mood.🙈

Products used : 
Primer @minisoindia 01 White
Concealer @maybelline 20 Sand
Foundation @maybelline 128 Warm Nude
Blush @wetnwildbeauty Mellow Wine
Highlighter @sivannacolorsth 
Eye shadow @nickaknewyork Under The Sea
Mascara @maybelline 
Eye liner @lakmeindia 
Lipstick @amwayofficialindia
Attitude Matt Lipstick (Mauve Magic)

Song : Baby (Clean Bandit ft. Marina and Luis Fonsi)💣

If you like this then don’t forget to like, comment and share the video. It will help me reach more people.✨🌻

latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling a saree in four ways✨💣
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am highly obsessed with sarees and I always get excited whenever mom shows me her new sarees. This video will help you to wear a saree in four amazing ways which you can carry in parties and business meetings as well. These looks are pretty simple and yet fashionable.✨✨

First and last saree is from @flipkart and the rest two are from local shops. 

Look 1 : Wearing a chiffon saree as a skirt with a crop top. 

Look 2 : Wearing a zebra printed net saree with an off-shoulder top and then added a choker.

Look 3 : Wearing a chiffon saree with a maharani blouse.

Look 4 : Wearing a chiffon saree with a collared white shirt. 

If you like this video then do like, share and comment.✨🧡
Also, tell me which look you liked the most. 

My favourite look is the last one.✨🙈

Song : Saree Wali Girl (Girik Aman)💣✨

latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling a lehanga in four ways✨✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Due to this pandemic situation we aren’t going to enjoy shadi vibes as we used to , at least for this year. So, I thought to pick a lehanga which I bought last year for one of my relatives marriage. I personally don’t like too heavy clothes and this video is all about styling a heavy lehanga in subtle ways. 

Using mom’s blouses and dupattas for first three look and in the fourth look I have used a crop top also last one is my favourite.✨✨
This video has to be my favourite till now.❤️🥺

Song : Desi Girl (Sunidhi Chauhan, Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani and Shankar Mahadevan)
